  "2026-07-24T07:01:04.342Z",claude-code-agent,"Duplicate check: searched all statuses for the exact bundled all-package install timeout and extension-command signature. No canonical item exists; related package ecosystem,CI performance,and current release recovery work are linked."
  "2026-07-24T07:02:23.362Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: the unchanged real acceptance still installs all 15 bundled packages through wildcard and all aliases. It passes alone in 8.9-10.1 seconds; two full coverage runs measured 27.9-30.1 seconds under concurrent I/O. A test-local 45-second budget preserves global 30-second hang detection and every functional assertion."
  "2026-07-24T07:19:25.624Z",claude-code-agent,"Final evidence: linked 134-test extension owner suite passed; three subsequent complete coverage runs passed the unchanged real all-15-package install with the test-local 45-second budget. Final full run: 354 files, 6,212 tests, exact 100/100/100/100. Static quality preserves the global timeout and all assertions."
